<style>
.rbp-offers{--n:#0f172a;--b:#1d4ed8;--a:#d97706;--m:#475569;--l:#e2e8f0;--bg:#f8fafc;background:#fff;color:#0f172a}.rbp-offers *{box-sizing:border-box}.rbp-offers a{text-decoration:none;color:inherit}.rbp-offers-c{width:min(100% - 2.5rem,1180px);margin:auto}.rbp-offers-sec{padding:72px 0}.rbp-offers-muted{background:#f8fafc}.rbp-offers-hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#78350f);color:#fff}.rbp-offers-hero-in{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) minmax(280px,.42fr);gap:36px;align-items:center;padding:82px 0}.rbp-offers-ey{display:inline-flex;border-radius:999px;background:#fef3c7;color:#92400e;padding:7px 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase}.rbp-offers-hero .rbp-offers-ey{background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);color:#fde68a}.rbp-offers h1{margin:16px 0;color:#fff;font-size:clamp(38px,6vw,72px);line-height:1.02;font-weight:900}.rbp-offers h2{margin:12px 0;font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,48px);line-height:1.08;font-weight:900}.rbp-offers h3{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:20px}.rbp-offers p{color:#475569;line-height:1.7}.rbp-offers-hero p{color:#cbd5e1;font-size:18px}.rbp-offers-grid{display:grid;gap:18px}.rbp-offers-g2{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr))}.rbp-offers-g3{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr))}.rbp-offers-card{border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:18px;background:#fff;padding:24px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(15,23,42,.05)}.rbp-offers-hero-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.16);color:#fff}.rbp-offers-hero-card p{color:#cbd5e1}.rbp-offers-actions{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;margin-top:24px}.rbp-offers-btn{display:inline-flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;border-radius:12px;padding:13px 16px;font-weight:900;border:1px solid rgba(15,23,42,.14);background:#fff;color:#334155}.rbp-offers-btn--primary{background:#d97706;border-color:#d97706;color:#fff}.rbp-offers-badge{display:inline-flex;border-radius:999px;padding:5px 10px;background:#f1f5f9;color:#334155;font-size:12px;font-weight:900}.rbp-offers-price{font-weight:900;color:#0f172a}.rbp-offers-list{display:grid;gap:14px;margin:18px 0 0;padding:0;list-style:none}.rbp-offers-list li{display:grid;grid-template-columns:24px 1fr;gap:10px}.rbp-offers-list li:before{content:"";width:18px;height:18px;margin-top:4px;border-radius:999px;background:#fef3c7}.rbp-offers-cta{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#d97706,#0f172a);border-radius:22px;padding:36px;color:#fff}.rbp-offers-cta h2,.rbp-offers-cta p{color:#fff}@media(max-width:900px){.rbp-offers-hero-in,.rbp-offers-g2,.rbp-offers-g3{grid-template-columns:1fr}.rbp-offers-btn{width:100%}.rbp-offers-sec{padding:56px 0}}
</style>
<div class="rbp-offers">
<section class="rbp-offers-hero"><div class="rbp-offers-c rbp-offers-hero-in"><div><span class="rbp-offers-ey">Partner Offers</span><h1>Curated partner offers for Australian SMEs.</h1><p>Browse offer pathways that are ready for enquiry while final terms, eligibility and partner details are confirmed before activation.</p><div class="rbp-offers-actions"><a class="rbp-offers-btn rbp-offers-btn--primary" href="#rbp-offers-list">Browse offers</a><a class="rbp-offers-btn" href="/pages/claim-offer">Claim an offer</a><a class="rbp-offers-btn" href="/pages/contact?inquiry=partner">Partner with us</a></div></div><aside class="rbp-offers-card rbp-offers-hero-card"><h3>Launch-readiness guardrails</h3><p>Offers require confirmed partner status, terms, eligibility, pricing language, CTA and disclosure before being treated as active.</p></aside></div></section>
<section class="rbp-offers-sec" id="rbp-offers-list"><div class="rbp-offers-c"><span class="rbp-offers-ey">Featured partner offers</span><h2>Current enquiry-ready offer pathways.</h2><div class="rbp-offers-grid rbp-offers-g2">
<article class="rbp-offers-card"><span class="rbp-offers-badge">Software</span><h3>Business productivity platform</h3><p>Curated productivity software offer for business operations. Full terms, inclusions and partner details are confirmed after enquiry.</p><p class="rbp-offers-price">Pricing confirmed after enquiry.</p><a class="rbp-offers-btn" href="/pages/claim-offer?offer=productivity-platform">Enquire about offer</a></article>
<article class="rbp-offers-card"><span class="rbp-offers-badge">Member pricing</span><h3>Premium member service opportunity</h3><p>Selected partner service opportunity for approved Premium Members, subject to eligibility and partner confirmation.</p><p class="rbp-offers-price">Member pricing.</p><a class="rbp-offers-btn" href="/pages/member-benefits">Review member access</a></article>
<article class="rbp-offers-card"><span class="rbp-offers-badge">Finance</span><h3>Business finance tool offer</h3><p>Business finance or accounting tool pathway. Finance outcomes and credits are subject to provider assessment and approval.</p><p class="rbp-offers-price">Available after enquiry.</p><a class="rbp-offers-btn" href="/pages/claim-offer?offer=business-finance-tool">Enquire about offer</a></article>
<article class="rbp-offers-card"><span class="rbp-offers-badge">Resources</span><h3>Business resource package</h3><p>Partner resource package pathway for business owners who need practical tools, templates or implementation resources.</p><p class="rbp-offers-price">Quote on request.</p><a class="rbp-offers-btn" href="/pages/claim-offer?offer=business-resource-package">Request details</a></article>
</div></div></section>
<section class="rbp-offers-sec rbp-offers-muted"><div class="rbp-offers-c rbp-offers-grid rbp-offers-g2"><div><span class="rbp-offers-ey">How it works</span><h2>How to access a partner offer.</h2><ul class="rbp-offers-list"><li>Choose an offer pathway and submit an enquiry.</li><li>RBP confirms eligibility, offer availability and required details.</li><li>The partner connection or claim process proceeds only when terms are clear.</li></ul></div><div class="rbp-offers-card"><h3>Before a public offer goes live</h3><p>Each public offer needs active status, public visibility, final short and full descriptions, confirmed terms, disclosure, SEO metadata, category, checked CTA URL, active partner status, sort order and approved imagery where available.</p></div></div></section>
<section class="rbp-offers-sec"><div class="rbp-offers-c"><div class="rbp-offers-cta"><h2>Need help choosing an offer?</h2><p>Use the claim page or contact RBP with your business need and the offer pathway you are interested in.</p><div class="rbp-offers-actions"><a class="rbp-offers-btn" href="/pages/claim-offer">Claim Offer</a><a class="rbp-offers-btn" href="/pages/offers-by-categories">Offers By Categories</a><a class="rbp-offers-btn" href="/pages/contact">Contact RBP</a></div></div></div></section>
</div>
